snippet.title: Racket Club | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Racket Club, a multiplayer game that reinvents the idea of pickup sports by connecting players from all over the world to have fun together in an all-new sport designed from the ground-up for VR play. Stay tuned as more details about Racket Club step onto the court in 2023. 

http://www.resolutiongames.com/racketclub
#vrgame #ResolutionGames
